nard\r\nAmersfoort (NL) : Centre d’Art moderne\r\nNeuchâtel (CH) : Galerie 2016\r\nTegelen (NL) : Tiendschuur Museum\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Jean Fontaine', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-30 19:53:49', '2015-08-30 18:53:49', '', 41, 'http://localhost:8888/2015/08/30/41-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
